{"tid":1152721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當撈侵又出口術: 今鋪你唔簽，等我連任下年再加！","createTime":"2019-05-13T07:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T07:28:06.000Z","uid":191338,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd433a8d9e5075996a9a33aafd6313950ab167b","tid":1152721,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:09:06.000Z","msg":"Trump tells China: reach a deal now before I offer a far worse one<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3009895/donald-trump-warns-china-reach-trade-deal-now-or-face-far\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fdiplomacy%2Farticle%2F3009895%2Fdonald-trump-warns-china-reach-trade-deal-now-or-face-far&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihEYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=c20c9189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3009895/donald-trump-warns-china-reach-trade-deal-now-or-face-far</a><br />\n<br />\n當撈侵又出口術<br />\n如果中囯揼波鐘，等佢下屆連任後會徵更多關稅<br />\n而家已經由10%加到25%，成200億<br />\n不過美國跟開obama個前副總統拜登又話中囯其實唔係同美國鬥<br />\n民主黨嘅佢原來係4月25已經出左片競選2020美國總統<br />\n唔知共和黨嘅侵侵下屆有幾多成機會連任<br />\n<br />\n睇返啲數據原來中囯2002年打後GDP開始飛，不過咁多年都未過到美國，到當撈侵任內開始收窄距離<br />\n<br />\n粗鐵出口量中囯由1998年開始已經拋離美國，完全冇得追<br />\n貨物出口量2007年係分水嶺，2009年後跑贏美國<br />\n汽車零件出口量2008年係分水嶺，之後大幅拋離美國<br />\n外債投資中囯好似唔興玩呢味，同美國大起大落完全係兩個玩法"},{"pid":"91bd398f202f32f2fcb8d2a5ba4ed616cd609c33","tid":1152721,"uid":117032,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"連到先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfca39b307d27a1bcd67bbe06a121c9195c87475","tid":1152721,"uid":191338,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQNFBiY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQNFBiY.jpg&h=01ad3f48&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}